## DBsubject(Calculus - single variable)
## DBchapter(Infinite sequences and series)
## DBsection(Taylor series)
## Institution(University of Michigan)
## Author(Gavin LaRose)
## Level(4)
## MO(1)
## TitleText1('Calculus')
## TitleText2('Calculus')
